description:
Deep within the mountain's dark heart, awaited the King of the Dead, a figure shrouded in ancient majesty and embittered grievance. The king, clad in spectral armour and crowned with the weight of countless ages, stood defiant. His eyes, burning with an unearthly light, regarded the supposed heir of Isildur™ with a mix of pride and scorn.
Behold the King of the Dead, an awe-inspiring 1:6 scale statue meticulously crafted by our master artisans. Emerging from the haunting depths of the Paths of the Dead, this spectral monarch commands a chilling gaze and haunting visage. Every detail, from the intricately sculpted armour adorned with ancient, tarnished symbols to the otherworldly glow in his piercing eyes, speaks of a cursed destiny and unyielding power.

In life, he was a king; in death, he is a legend. Bound by an unbroken oath, he stands as a testament to honour and the dire consequences of broken promises. Let his presence in your collection serve as a reminder of the eternal struggle between duty and redemption. With an aura of unsettling majesty, this statue captures the very essence of the undead sovereign, making it a must-have for any dedicated fan of Middle-earth's timeless saga.

Embrace the legacy. Command the legend. Own the King of the Dead.

- 1:6 scale;
- Limited Edition of 700 pieces;
- Depicts the King of the Dead as seen in The Return of the King™;
- Transparent material and expert paint application creates a ghostly spectral glow;
- Digitally sculpted by Fabio Paiva with references from the original movie costume.


Dimensions: 40 x 42,5 x 26,6 cm
